{"tid":597301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中概股熱】愛奇藝、Bilibili赴美上市 集資24及5億美元","createTime":"2018-03-18T13:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T02:09:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"26574f6932ea36a84f1e112f658ca416f066552a","tid":597301,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"中概股赴美上市潮不斷，串流影片平台愛奇藝及Bilibili計劃納斯達克交易所上市，分別集資24億及5.25億美元。<br />\n<br />\n百度旗下的愛奇藝至2月底有6010萬用戶，其中98%為付費用戶，愛奇藝指將以發表包括戲劇等原創内容為發展方向。愛奇藝去年收入升至27億美元，但全年仍虧5.74億美元。其上市安排行為高盛、花旗及美銀。<br />\n<br />\nBilibili用戶超過八成為90後或千禧世代，每月活躍用戶為7180萬，去年收入為3.79億美元，全年虧蝕2.8億美元。摩根士丹利、摩根大通及美銀為上市安排行。<br />\n<br />\n兩新股將以同股不同權方式上市，去年共有21中國公司在美上市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180317/57960093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57960093&d=7qpAz7OK7EGI94xZuW%2BYpARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8704b4c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57960093&h=6ddb1411\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180317/57960093</a>"},{"pid":"7236dbee66e90456bbcd83a7fc4029a0e03f7cd3","tid":597301,"uid":77196,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔係A股上，又話鄰國強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406022da8738c86eb8cbe23761a9bf1859c8daad","tid":597301,"uid":25424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7236dbee66e90456bbcd83a7fc4029a0e03f7cd3","tid":597301,"uid":77196,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"點解唔係A股上，又話鄰國強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/